com.sap.integration.anywhere.dto

Interface IAnwDto

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AnwCustomerDto, AnwProductDto

    public interface IAnwDto
    Interface used for unification of functionality. Not all SAP Anywhere objects have implemented this functionality - only Customer and Product. It was created only for demo purposes, that it is possible to unify functionality on SAP Anywhere objects.
